Leaf blocks​

Thematic breaks​

The tokenizer @yozora/tokenizer-thematic-break already supports processing this type of data.

Example 13-31​

#13
yozora
  
pretty-json
  
1
2
3
***
---
___

ATX headings​

The tokenizer @yozora/tokenizer-heading already supports processing this type of data.

Example 32-49​

#32

pretty-json

2
3
4
5
6

## foo
### foo
#### foo
##### foo
###### foo
